{"tid":1719501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[純猜測] 琴晚開會好可能就係共識發動全面民眾鬥民眾","createTime":"2019-11-14T06:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T07:19:55.000Z","uid":81236,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d44cbf853dcbf834c81b9a794c92be5f81a49312","tid":1719501,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:06:26.000Z","msg":"最大既signal就係保皇黨出黎講全民抗暴<br />\n<br />\n一直以黎政府都係強調警隊執法，呼籲市民割席<br />\n<br />\n但一夜之後居然變調成抗暴自救？<br />\n<br />\n呼籲藍絲出黎以不同手段解決<br />\n<br />\n根本就係發動民眾鬥民眾<br />\n<br />\n琴日由藍絲發動既打鬥已經害死左呀伯<br />\n<br />\n今日上水再次發生由藍絲發動既有組織打鬥<br />\n<br />\n會唔會就係政府已經默許藍絲用暴力手段恫嚇市民？<br />\n<br />\n到底係邊個容許佢地咁做？<br />\n比721更恐怖既係係日光日白下發動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於敵方發動民眾鬥民眾<br />\n<br />\n不論你係文宣、勇武、冷氣軍師都要留意<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民眾鬥民鬥最大既力量係轉視線轉移</span><br />\n<br />\n將對抗政府既力量變成對抗藍絲<br />\n<br />\n請香港人請認清楚<br />\n<br />\n發動民眾鬥民眾極有可能令721日間化及平常化<br />\n<br />\n請咁多位一定要團結一致<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「以武制黑」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一定要清楚指出係黑社會及有可能由政府發動既民眾鬥民眾<br />\n<br />\n會令香港人陷入藍絲，黑社會治港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">即使文宣藍絲都要強調因果關係</span><br />\n<br />\n如果香港人唔還擊就會釀成再一場既721恐襲<br />\n<br />\n唔反抗就會有更多香港人被斬<br />\n<br />\n今日仲要捉左個女仔，好彩最後無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但想強調，你唔知道下個被捉既女仔會唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特別係由KBS都出左報導有最少兩單既女手足被黑警強姦<br />\n<br />\n如果連黑警都係咁，呢班黑社會你更加唔洗諗佢地會有事<br />\n<br />\n佢地極有可能已經被人默許咁做<br />\n<br />\n香港人係自衛反擊，以武制黑！<br />\n<br />\n係一群願意企出黎既勇武擊退黑社會，保護左香港人！"},{"pid":"cc258217d4b8368c58a60c8d51959249aa41641c","tid":1719501,"uid":36287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:07:32.000Z","msg":"警察無能<br />\n藍屍自救<br />\n分化埋佢地囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf86d75410a3bd36b43a20fd02ff317cac58ee7","tid":1719501,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:07:46.000Z","msg":"[文宣升級&mdash;要追上前線行動呀！]<br />\n解鎖新職業 &mdash; 郵差叔叔，速遞員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717313</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，手足，借個位，認同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發生好多事，好多怨案，令我地好嬲好嬲。但文宣一定要做足做好，我地係為正義而戰，我地從來都唔係暴徒！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arAivP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarAivP6.png&h=a9a1a627&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLZfgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLZfgM.jpg&h=20bdb60e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cdb7a3193d08fa848deceed4af002aeba5ecb32","tid":1719501,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:08:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當前重點係要將運動帶來嘅不便指向政府，並用深入淺出嘅方法同市民講，以爭取支持</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c6d02ed7863cc689a8d9f021c241505e094cd99d","tid":1719501,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cdb7a3193d08fa848deceed4af002aeba5ecb32","tid":1719501,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:08:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當前重點係要將運動帶來嘅不便指向政府，並用深入淺出嘅方法同市民講，以爭取支持</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:08:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>佢哋可以鼓動民眾 我哋都可以</strong></span>"},{"pid":"3320ca92457b23eaa98aa2de3398949c72a5ce5f","tid":1719501,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"呢個一定係靠街坊"},{"pid":"c3a876586bbeeb01d68891c6168400c834371c71","tid":1719501,"uid":54415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:10:13.000Z","msg":"宣傳吧, 而家對家係搞民鬥, 即係全民戰爭, 冇人可以絕對安全<br />\n著黑衫會俾人打<br />\n年青人俾人打<br />\n女仔一個行街隨時俾人捉<br />\n黑白兩道而家夾埋一齊玩, 你點揀"},{"pid":"89181583995dc2421cbdd27e6cf22858abf81101","tid":1719501,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:25:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2bd804a7c39c0390852ab392d27e4343812b1f89","tid":1719501,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"ousg"},{"pid":"dafcf3a78416d340c5dd5321e44b0b0c71ad36b8","tid":1719501,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:34:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dfece9e1053831b7e82f7b909ffc33ecd5e7f650","tid":1719501,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:47:27.000Z","msg":"建議係be water<br />\n<br />\n如果好明顯係黑幫攻擊既<br />\n1.夠手足&gt;開戰，全面進攻，但要留意附近有冇狗想引手足中計<br />\n2.唔夠手足&gt;撤，由佢地拆，等佢地走左再起<br />\n<br />\n但同時間，亦真係會有普通市民會走去參與，如果我地動手先，會好肉酸（中立或藍絲，純粹覺得眼前既路障阻到佢，其他人被塞wfc)<br />\n<br />\n1.嘗試勸服（其他替代方法）<br />\n2.可以考慮開一條線應付佢地，總之盡快耍走佢，唔好同佢纏擾太耐"},{"pid":"325a08147f5f53a4f4cd316635a9135fae521235","tid":1719501,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:47:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以武制黑</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0583688f7a7c959beb4e82942b08bf42db7ec9","tid":1719501,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:49:26.000Z","msg":"求下絲打們唔好出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾人綁架左就會係暗網內容<br />\n夾左上車就與世隔絕㗎喇！"},{"pid":"3844c216aaeb3f4784def7a86b3ce4a69130f03f","tid":1719501,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:09:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"73bdb4a94a80e72898439515a053b463ceee8322","tid":1719501,"uid":48057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019